Eddie Barth https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eddie_Barth 0 Eddie Barth (September 29, 1931 – May 28, 2010; born Edward Michael Bartholetti) was an American actor and voiceover artist. Barth earned the nickname "Mr. Gravel" for his raspy vocals in his voiceover work.
